Description: Fender's Nashville Telecaster blends classic sound and aesthetics with modern upgrades that enhance its overall performance. Its 12" radius fingerboard makes bends easy, while a contoured neck heel adds to the guitar's stellar feel, making high-fret access a breeze. Sonically, the Deluxe Nashville Telecaster is outfitted with three single-coil Vintage pickups and five-way switching, allowing for a more versatile tonal palette that your average Telecaster is capable of.
